article_title: Austrian Police Increase Security After Terror Warning
article_text:
BERLIN—Austrian police said Saturday they had strengthened security measures after receiving a warning from a “friendly” intelligence service about a possible terror attack in the days between Christmas and New Year’s.

In a statement, police in Vienna said the intelligence service had issued a warning to several European capitals in the days before Christmas that an attack involving explosives or shootings could take place in crowded...
